OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cfound unconscious in Belfast
OL,6,FA man is in a critical condition in
OL,7,Fhospital after being found unconscious
OL,8,Fin Belfast city centre.
OL,10,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,11,Fin the vicinity of Castle Place/Royal
OL,12,FAvenue at around 4.40pm on Saturday.
OL,14,FAn unconscious male was found at the
OL,15,Fscene and was tended to by ambulance
OL,16,Fstaff.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital and remains
OL,19,Fin a critical condition as of Sunday
OL,20,Fmorning, police said.
