OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cfound unconscious in Belfast
OL,6,FDetectives have appealed for
OL,7,Finformation from anyone as they work
OL,8,Fto establish the events leading up to
OL,9,Fthe incident.
OL,11,FThe PSNI said they are exploring a
OL,12,Fpossible link to an earlier assault
OL,13,Freported at 4.30pm, occurring in
OL,14,FCastle Place.
OL,16,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,17,Fcontact 101, quoting reference 1024 of
OL,18,F14/03/26.
